BodyName: Bronx Delegation of the New York City Council

Items.Title: Pursuant to Section 2403 of the New York City Charter, the members of the Council representing the Borough of The Bronx will meet to vote on the nomination of Sophia Reed for appointment to the Department for the Aging Advisory Council.
Items.MatterName: Members of the Council representing the Borough of The Bronx will meet to vote on the nomination of Sophia Reed for appointment to the Department for the Aging Advisory Council.
